<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Happy Birthday Rifa</title>

<style>

body{
margin:0;
padding:0;
height:100vh;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
background:linear-gradient(270deg,#ff758c,#ff7eb3,#ffd86f);
background-size:600% 600%;
animation:bgmove 12s infinite;
font-family: 'Segoe UI';
overflow:hidden;
}

@keyframes bgmove{
0%{background-position:0% 50%}
50%{background-position:100% 50%}
100%{background-position:0% 50%}
}

.container{
text-align:center;
color:white;
}

.envelope{
width:250px;
height:170px;
background:#fff;
position:relative;
margin:auto;
cursor:pointer;
border-radius:10px;
box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
}

.envelope:before{
content:"";
position:absolute;
width:0;
height:0;
border-left:125px solid transparent;
border-right:125px solid transparent;
border-bottom:85px solid #ff6b81;
top:-85px;
left:0;
}

.letter{
position:absolute;
background:white;
color:#333;
width:85%;
height:80%;
left:7%;
top:10%;
border-radius:10px;
padding:20px;
box-sizing:border-box;
opacity:0;
transform:translateY(30px);
transition:1s;
overflow:auto;
}

.open .letter{
opacity:1;
transform:translateY(-40px);
}

.title{
font-size:28px;
font-weight:bold;
margin-bottom:10px;
color:#ff4d6d;
}

.text{
font-size:16px;
line-height:1.6;
}

.hearts span{
position:absolute;
color:#ff4d6d;
font-size:20px;
animation:float 6s linear infinite;
}

@keyframes float{
0%{transform:translateY(0);opacity:1}
100%{transform:translateY(-800px);opacity:0}
}

.cake{
font-size:40px;
margin-top:20px;
animation:bounce 1.5s infinite;
}

@keyframes bounce{
0%,100%{transform:translateY(0)}
50%{transform:translateY(-10px)}
}

.footer{
margin-top:20px;
font-size:14px;
opacity:0.8;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="hearts">
<span style="left:10%">❤</span>
<span style="left:30%">❤</span>
<span style="left:50%">❤</span>
<span style="left:70%">❤</span>
<span style="left:90%">❤</span>
</div>

<div class="container">

<h1>🎉 Happy Birthday Rifa 🎉</h1>

<div class="envelope" onclick="openLetter(this)">
<div class="letter">

<div class="title">Dear Rifa 💌</div>

<div class="text">
Today is a special day — <b>July 14</b>.  
I just want to wish you a very happy birthday.  

May Allah bless your life with happiness, success, and peace.  
I hope your dreams come true and your future becomes bright.  

Stay happy, stay strong, and keep smiling always.  

✨ May your life be full of success.  
✨ May every step take you closer to your dreams.  
✨ May happiness always find you.  

Once again...  

<b>Happy Birthday Rifa 🎂</b>
</div>

<div class="cake">🎂</div>

</div>
</div>

<div class="footer">
Click the letter to open your birthday message 💖
</div>

</div>

<script>

function openLetter(el){
el.classList.toggle("open")
}

</script>

</body>
</html>
